e5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nhu\u1ed9m v\u00e0ng c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 ngang t\u00e0i ngang s\u1ee9c, hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. C\u1ea3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Emil Forsbergst \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Vikings gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn th\u00eam chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf d\u00e0nh cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Michael Lang, v\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/074832-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t n\u1eef C\u0110V xinh \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CDV Thuy Dien vs Thuy Si\" title=\"C\u0110V Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/075151-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<