         </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thuyen-truong-thuy-si-giai-thich-nguy-nhan-that-bai-421-190328.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/thuyen-truong-thuy-si-giai-thich-nguy-nhan-that-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thuyen-truong-thuy-si-giai-thich-nguy-nhan-that-bai-421-190328.html\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Petkovic chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-thuy-sy-vs-thuy-dien-461-190299.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/224228-3.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-thuy-sy-vs-thuy-dien-461-190299.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 1-0 t\u1ed1i 3/7, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u00edt h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-arsenal-bi-chi-trich-tham-te-trong-tran-thua-thuy-dien-421-190316.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/chinh-thuc-man-utd-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-aicungkhongbietlaai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-arsenal-bi-chi-trich-tham-te-trong-tran-thua-thuy-dien-421-190316.html\">Sao Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 trong tr\u1eadn thua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man United &ndash; c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Phil Neville l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Xhaka sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"870","checkdouble":"190333"},{"date":"08:28 04/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-tran-colombia-vs-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00e1 im \u1eafng, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2. \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, Harry Kane d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trung v\u1ec7 Mina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, k\u00e9o cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u00e2n n\u00e3o. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng (Henderson) tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pickford (v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang), qua \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng James Rodriguez l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng v\u1eeba v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Nhung-hinh-anh-tran-dau-Colombia-vs-Anh-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Anh tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u0110V Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/081929-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Colombia t\u1ea1i Moscow</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; 